%3Bmulti-tasking%26quot%3B%20and%20sometimes%20would%20be%20on%20the%20phone%20at%20the%20same%20time%20he%20signed%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20nine%20of%20Trump's%20personally-signed%20checks%20%E2%80%94%20reimbursing%20his%20then%20attorney%2C%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20in%20monthly%20installments%20for%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20Stormy%20Daniels%20%E2%80%94%20are%20the%20most%20damning%20evidence%20in%20the%20GOP%20frontrunner's%20Manhattan%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testimony%20was%20elicited%20during%20Graff's%20cross-examination%20by%20Trump%20attorney%20Susan%20Necheles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAm%20I%20correct%20that%20when%20he%20would%20sign%20checks%20he%20was%20also%20multi-tasking%3F%26quot%3B%20Necheles%20asked%20Graff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20on%20occasion%2C%26quot%3B%20Graff%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20would%20see%20him%20often%20on%20the%20phone%20when%20he%20was%20signing%20checks%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20pressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20phone-in-one-hand%2C%20Sharpie-in-the-other%20multitasking%20didn't%20happen%20often%2C%20Graff%20told%20Necheles%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20did%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20common%20it%20was%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20assistant%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nine%20checks%20are%20the%20only%20records%20bearing%20Trump's%20signature%20out%20of%2034%20checks%2C%20invoices%2C%20and%20business-ledger%20records%20he%20allegedly%20falsified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriday's%20testimony%20suggests%20that%20the%20defense%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Trump%20himself%20if%20he%20takes%20the%20stand%20%E2%80%94%20may%20be%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20distracted%20by%20running%20the%20country%20throughout%202017%2C%20as%20he%20affixed%20his%20signature%20to%20nine%20monthly%20hush-money%20reimbursement%20checks%20made%20out%20out%20to%20Cohen%2C%20his%20attorney%20and%20%26quot%3Bfixer%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump's%20personal%20check%20for%20%2435%2C000%2C%20paid%20to%20his%20then-lawyer%20Michael%20Cohen%20and%20key%20evidence%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhush%20money%26quot%3B%20scheme%20under%20investigation%20by%20Manhattan%20prosecutors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63d92f85526500001938ed47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20Trump's%20personal%20check%20for%20%2435%2C000%2C%20paid%20to%20his%20then-lawyer%20Michael%20Cohen.%3Cp%3EHouse%20Oversight%20Committee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg%20alleges%20that%20the%20nine%20checks%20%E2%80%94%20one%20each%20for%20the%20months%20April%20through%20December%20%E2%80%94%20were%20cut%20from%20Trump's%20personal%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20month%2C%20another%20check%20was%20sent%20through%20Fed-%20Ex%20Fed-exed%20from%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20to%20the%20White%20House%20for%20Trump's%20signature%2C%20Bragg%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Trump%20signed%20each%20check%2C%20it%20would%20be%20sent%20through%20FedEx%20back%20to%20the%20Trump%20Organization's%20Trump%20Tower%20headquarters%2C%20scanned%20into%20the%20company%20records%2C%20and%20then%20cut%20and%20mailed%20to%20Cohen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20checks%20reimbursed%20Cohen%20for%20having%20directly%20paid%20Daniels%20%24130%2C000%20to%20stay%20silent%20just%2011%20days%20before%20the%20November%2C%202016%20election%2C%20prosecutors%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20direct%20examination%2C%20Graff%20gave%20some%20damaging%2C%20or%20at%20least%20cringe-worthy%2C%20testimony%2C%20telling%20jurors%20that%20as%20part%20of%20her%20Trump%20Organization%20duties%20she%20kept%20Windows%20Outlook%20contact%20cards%20with%20phone%20numbers%20for%20Stormy%20Daniels%20and%20Karen%20McDougal%20on%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20Trump%20falsified%20business%20records%20in%20an%20election-influencing%20conspiracy%20to%20keep%20Daniels%20(a%20porn%20star)%2C%20and%20McDougal%20(a%20former%20Playboy%20Bunny)%2C%20from%20going%20public%20with%20allegations%20of%20having%20sexual%20liaisons%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniels%20was%20wired%20%24130%2C000%20in%20hush%20money%20just%2011%20days%20before%20Trump%20won%20the%202016%20election.%20Trump%20denies%20sleeping%20with%20Daniels%20and%20McDougal%20or%20cooking%20his%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20create%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20Manhattan%20prosecutor%2C%20Susan%20Hoffinger%2C%20asked%20Graff%2C%20as%20People's%20Exhibit%2083%20was%20displayed%20on%20four%20large%20screens%20in%20the%20courtroom.%20Each%20screen%20showed%20an%20Outlook%20card%20for%20Daniels%2C%20her%20cellphone%20number%20blacked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20I%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20answered%20Graff%2C%20who%20said%20she%20could%20not%20recall%20a%20single%20instance%20in%2034%20years%20working%20for%20Trump%20when%20he%20used%20a%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20defense%20lawyer%20Susan%20Necheles%20used%20her%20cross%20examination%20to%20ask%20a%20series%20of%20softball%20questions%20that%20allowed%20the%20loyal%20ex-assistant%20to%20speak%20glowingly%20about%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20he%20a%20good%20boss%3F%26quot%3B%20Necheles%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20he%20was%20a%20fair%20and%20%E2%80%94%20what's%20the%20word%20I'm%20looking%20for%3F%20%E2%80%94%20respectful%20boss%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Graff%20told%20jurors%20of%20working%20alongside%20Trump%20in%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20headquarters%20on%20the%2025th-floor%20of%20Trump%20Tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20asked%20about%20her%20family%2C%20told%20her%20to%20go%20home%20when%20she%20worked%20late%2C%20and%20gave%20her%20a%20good%20seat%20at%20his%20inauguration%2C%20the%20assistant%20sa