-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0BYPYRH4F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESony%20A95L%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20perform%20a%20bit%20better%20in%20certain%20areas%20(and%20worse%20in%20others)%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20doubt%20the%20Samsung%20S95D%20is%20a%20top%20contender%20in%20the%20premium%20TV%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3EA%20new%20benchmark%20for%20OLED%20TV%20brightness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221652%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95D%20OLED%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20popping%20champagne%20bottle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d82ff3f923f7dab0420bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221239%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95D%20can%20get%20incredibly%20bright%20while%20maintaining%20an%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio%20with%20deep%20black%20levels.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Samsung%20S95D%20is%20a%20picture%20performance%20champ%20with%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20that%20buyers%20should%20expect%20from%20a%20TV%20in%20this%20price%20range.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20QD-OLED%20panel%20(OLED%20with%20quantum%20dots)%2C%20the%20display%20offers%20pixel-level%20contrast%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20vibrant%20colors%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20exceptional%20high-dynamic-range%20(HDR)%20images.%20And%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20the%20S95D%20is%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20I've%20ever%20measured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20the%20TV%20in%20Filmmaker%20mode%20for%20testing%20purposes%2C%20which%20offers%20the%20most%20accurate%20picture%20settings.%20Using%20an%20X-Rite%20colorimeter%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20peak%20brightness%20of%20around%201%2C700%20nits%20on%20a%2010%25%20HDR%20test%20pattern%20(a%20white%20box%20that%20takes%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20screen).%20That's%20about%20350%20nits%20more%20than%20last%20year's%20version%20of%20this%20TV%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-s95c-oled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S95C%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20about%20200%20nits%20more%20than%20the%20S95D's%20top%20competitors%2C%20including%20the%20LG%20G4.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20S95D%20can%20only%20hit%201%2C700%20nits%20in%20short%20bursts%20before%20dimming%20significantly.%20On%20the%2010%25%20test%20pattern%2C%20the%20TV%20gradually%20fell%20to%20around%20750%20nits%20and%20dropped%20more%20over%20time.%20I've%20seen%20this%20kind%20of%20behavior%20on%20a%20few%20other%20OLED%20TVs%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20extreme%20on%20this%20model%20than%20on%20competitors.%20But%20while%20that%20might%20sound%20like%20a%20major%20drawback%2C%20it%20actually%20isn't%20that%20big%20of%20a%20deal.%20It's%20rare%20for%20HDR%20videos%20to%20call%20for%20sustained%20brightness%20that%20high.%20Most%20highlights%20that%20actually%20need%20to%20get%20very%20bright%20(like%20a%20gunshot%20or%20an%20explosion%20in%20a%20movie)%20only%20flash%20on%20the%20screen%20quickly%2C%20and%20the%20S95D%20can%20handle%20those%20instances%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20stands%2C%20the%20S95D's%20brightness%20capabilities%20help%20the%20TV%20produce%20a%20vibrant%20image%20and%20give%20you%20plenty%20of%20headroom%20to%20pump%20up%20luminance%20and%20adjust%20settings%20to%20suit%20spaces%20that%20let%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20light.%20It%20also%20helps%20the%20TV%20display%20high-brightness%20HDR%20videos%20closer%20to%20how%20filmmakers%20intended%20them%20to%20look.%20And%20the%20results%20are%20fantastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95D%20delivers%20impressive%20image%20quality%20when%20watching%20actual%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20During%20my%20testing%20session%2C%20I%20sampled%20various%20film%20sequences%20I%20use%20across%20all%20the%20TVs%20I%20evaluate%2C%20including%20scenes%20from%204K%20Blu-ray%20discs%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAquaman%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BEx%20Machina%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLa%20La%20Land%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20HDR%20streaming%20demos%20from%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20a%20frog%20displayed%20on%20a%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c118a0dfb1341e9fff103%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuantum%20dots%20help%20the%20S95D%20produce%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20vibrant%20colors.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20high-quality%204K%20material%2C%20the%20TV%20simply%20stuns.%20Fine%20details%20are%20sharp%2C%20contrast%20is%20high%2C%20and%20saturation%20is%20rich%20with%20bold%20hues%20that%20pop%20from%20the%20screen%20when%20called%20for.%20That%20said%2C%20while%20most%20demo%20material%20came%20through%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20bright%20saturation%20I%20expect%20from%20a%20QD-OLED%20with%20such%20high%20color%20volume%2C%20the%20climactic%20battle%20in%20%26quot%3BAquaman%26quot%3B%20looked%20a%20bit%20more%20subdued%20than%20I%20was%20expecting.%20I%20have%20a%20hunch%20something%20wonky%20was%20going%20on%20with%20the%20settings%2C%20so%20I'll%20revisit%20that%20sequence%20when%20I%20conduct%20extended%20testing%20and%20update%20this%20section%20with%20additional%20findings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20great%20showcase%20for%20the%20S95D's%20contrast%20performance%20in%20a%20dark%20room.%20Bright%20specular%20highlights%2C%20like%20a%20police%20officer's%20flashlight%2C%20pop%20off%20the%20screen%20while%20black%20levels%20remain%20deep.%20And%20since%20each%20pixel%20on%20the%20TV's%20OLED%20panel%20can%20dim%20and%20brighten%20independently%2C%20the%20S95D%20is%20completely%20free%20from%20the%20kind%20of%20backlight%20blooming%20issues%20you'd%20see%20on%20competing%20QLED%20TVs.%20With%20the%20lights%20on%2C%20however%2C%20this%20scene%20reveals%20some%20of%20the%20drawbacks%20associated%20with%20the%20S95D's%20matte-screen%20finish%20(more%20on%20that%20in%20the%20next%20section).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95D%20handles%20gradients%20smoothly%20with%20minimal%20instances%20of%20banding.%20Our%20go-to%20real-world%20test%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BEx%20Machina%26quot%3B%20only%20revealed%20tiny%20hints%20of%20banding%20in%20the%20extreme%20red%20shades%20around%20one%20character's%20shoulder%2C%20which%20is%20about%20equal%20to%20what%20I've%20seen%20on%20other%20high-end%20sets.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20sampled%20a%20few%20regular%20HD%20videos%20in%20standard%20dynamic%20range%20and%20some%20lower-quality%20streams%20from%20Samsung's%20free%20live%20TV%20service%2C%20Samsung%20TV%20Plus%2C%20and%20the%20S95D%20handled%20them%20well.%20That%20said%2C%20upscaling%20isn't%20quite%20as%20good%20as%20you'll%20see%20on%20Sony's%20flagship%20TVs%2C%20so%20you'll%20get%20a%20slightly%20softer%20image%20with%20more%20source-related%20flaws%20visible.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENote%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20S95D%20is%20available%20in%2055-%2C%2065-%2C%20and%2077-inch%20screen%20sizes%2C%20and%20they%20all%20offer%20the%20same%20display%20specifications.%20Samsung%20says%20all%20S95D%20models%20being%20shipped%20to%20retailers%20in%20the%20US%20right%20now%20use%20QD-OLED%20panels.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20the%20brand%20could%20sell%20versions%20of%20its%202024%20OLED%20TVs%20with%20WRGB%20panels%20instead.%20WRGB%20OLED%20panels%20don't%20incorporate%20quantum%20dots%2C%20so%20any%20S95D%20TV%20with%20that%20panel%20type%20would%20offer%20reduced%20color%20and%20brightness%20capabilities.%20Again%2C%20this%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20concern%20for%20anyone%20shopping%20for%20an%20S95D%20now%2C%20but%20I'll%20update%20this%20review%20if%20WRGB%20variants%20end%20up%20being%20released%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Matte%20screen%5C%22%3EThe%20matte%20screen%20nearly%20eliminates%20reflections%2C%20but%20black%20levels%20suffer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV's%20impressive%20reflection-handling%20while%20displaying%20a%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrxi.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c0f4623b29110d303d048%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20might%20be%20able%20to%20make%20out%20a%20faint%20hint%20of%20my%20reflection%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20screen%2C%20but%20the%20S95D%20eliminates%20the%20mirror-like%20effect%20that%20other%20OLED%20TVs%20have.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20S95D's%20most%20striking%20features%20is%20its%20new%20glare-free%20screen%20filter.%20Virtually%20every%20other%20TV%20sold%20right%20now%20(including%20last%20year's%20S95C)%20uses%20a%20glossy%20finish%20that%20causes%20a%20reflective%20quality%20when%20you%20watch%20TV%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%20But%2C%20the%20S95D%20has%20a%20matte%20finish%20that%20significantly%20reduces%20glare%20and%20reflections.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20almost%20eliminates%20them%20entirely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeriously%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20screens%20I've%20seen%20for%20handling%20glare.%20The%20only%20other%20notable%20TV%20with%20a%20similar%20matte%20coating%20is%20Samsung's%20own%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-64254-20%26h%3Df7df0e552a9e49448766c5824ae0df8b9926cf8d4da3b626dc72102b8bdd11df%26postID%3D662c0b964afb95b2cc3f2a30%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-s95d-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0CV9K9BR7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrame%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20model%20can't%20match%20the%20S95D's%20overall%20image%20quality.%20And%20when%20you%20add%20in%20the%20TV's%20high%20brightness%20capabilities%2C%20the%20S95D%20cements%20itself%20as%20a%20great%20option%20for%20rooms%20that%20let%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20light.%20However%2C%20the%20TV's%20glare-free%20screen%20does%20have%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20black-level%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20having%20the%20deep%2C%20inky%20quality%20that%20OLED%20black%20levels%20are%20known%20for%2C%20blacks%20look%20a%20bit%20elevated%2C%20hazy%2C%20and%20gray%20when%20watching%20TV%20with%20the%20lights%20on.%20This%20was%20very%20evident%20when%20viewing%20dark%20scenes%2C%20like%20the%20opening%20sequence%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20being%20displayed%20on%20a%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c106410dfcda409641b7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20matte%20screen%20is%20great%20for%20reducing%20glare%20in%20bright%20rooms%2C%20but%20it%20can%20give%20black%20levels%20a%20gray%20and%20slightly%20hazy%20look.%20(Note%3A%20The%20camera%20exaggerates%20this%20effect%20so%20it's%20a%20bit%20less%20noticeable%20in%20person).%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20bit%20torn%20about%20this%20side%20effect%2C%20and%20while%20I%20know%20that%20many%20buyers%20will%20love%20the%20perks%20of%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%2C%20I%20lean%20toward%20preferring%20a%20glossier%20look%20that%20preserves%20black%20levels.%20I%20studied%20filmmaking%20and%20am%20a%20huge%20movie%20buff%2C%20so%20picture%20accuracy%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20a%20TV%20to%20me.%20Deep%20black%20levels%20are%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20preserving%20the%20intended%20look%20of%20a%20movie%2C%20so%20the%20matte%20screen's%20negative%20impact%20on%20contrast%20is%20disappointing.%20That%20said%2C%20there's%20no%20denying%20how%20well%20the%20filter%20works%20at%20reducing%20reflections%2C%20so%20if%20you%20have%20a%20big%20issue%20with%20glare%20in%20your%20room%2C%20the%20pros%20here%20will%20outweigh%20the%20cons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20matte%20screen%2C%20the%20S95D's%20design%20looks%20a%20lot%20like%20the%202023%20S95C%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20a%20bad%20thing.%20This%202024%20model%20carries%20over%20its%20predecessor's%20uniformly%20thin%20profile%20and%20has%20a%20similar%20pedestal%20stand%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20One%20Connect%20box%2C%20which%20houses%20all%20of%20the%20TV's%20video%20and%20audio%20ports%20instead%20of%20having%20them%20built%20into%20the%20panel.%20Build%20quality%20is%20also%20sturdy%20and%20a%20clear%20step%20up%20from%20cheaper%20designs%20used%20on%20sets%20from%20more%20budget-friendly%20brands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20features%5C%22%3EThe%20smart%20TV%20interface%20is%20solid%2C%20and%20you%20can%20stream%20Xbox%20games%20with%20a%20subscription%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95D%20on%20a%20TV%20stand%20in%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660c2ab93f923f7dab03a1e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221309%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamsung's%20smart%20TV%20interface%20is%20easy%20to%20navigate.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung's%20smart%20TV%20interface%2C%20which%20runs%20on%20the%20Tizen%20operating%20system%2C%20has%20received%20a%20few%20minor%20design%20tweaks%20for%20a%20slightly%20more%20streamlined%20look%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20similar%20experience%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20offering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigation%20through%20menus%20was%20snappy%20during%20my%20initial%20time%20with%20the%20TV%20and%20seemed%20a%20bit%20more%20consistent%20than%20last%20year's%20model.%20Some%20apps%20can%20still%20take%20a%20little%20longer%20to%20load%20than%20they%20do%20on%20dedicated%20streaming%20devices%20I've%20tested%2C%20but%20I%20like%20how%20there's%20now%20a%20loading%20bar%20that%20appears%20when%20opening%20apps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20last%20year's%20model%2C%20the%20interface%20features%20a%20dedicated%20Gaming%20Hub%20section%2C%20and%20Samsung%20is%20still%20the%20only%20TV%20brand%20to%20offer%20built-in%20support%20for%20the%20Xbox%20app.%20This%20means%20you%20can%20stream%20Xbox%20games%20directly%20to%20the%20TV%20without%20a%20console%2C%20so%20long%20as%20you%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%3EXbox%20Game%20Pass%20Ultimate%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20Bluetooth%20controller.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Forza%20Horizon%205%20being%20played%20on%20a%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c110e23b29110d303d191%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20have%20an%20S95D%20and%20a%20Game%20Pass%20Ultimate%20plan%2C%20you%20can%20stream%20titles%20like%20Forza%20Horizon%205%20without%20an%20Xbox%20console.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EXbox%20streaming%20performance%20relies%20heavily%20on%20your%20internet%20connection%20and%20is%20limited%20to%20HD%20resolution%20in%20standard%20dynamic%20range%20with%20two-channel%20sound%2C%20but%20the%20feature%20gets%20the%20job%20done.%20It's%20not%20how%20