20purchase%20this%20device%2C%20you'll%20also%20receive%20circular%20paper%20microfilters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20AeroPress%20involves%20numerous%20pieces%2C%20each%20item%20is%20small%20and%20lightweight%20enough%20to%20be%20easily%20transported.%20And%2C%20because%20the%20device%20is%20entirely%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20cracking%20or%20shattering%20a%20glass%20carafe.%20The%20AeroPress%20can%20easily%20live%20in%20an%20office%20desk%20drawer%2C%20a%20shared%20kitchen%20pantry%2C%20or%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20carry-on%20luggage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20assemble%20the%20AeroPress%2C%20drop%20the%20microfilter%20into%20the%20filter%20basket%20and%20twist%20the%20basket%20onto%20the%20brewing%20tube.%20The%20tube%20rests%20on%20top%20of%20your%20mug%20or%20whatever%20you're%20brewing%20into%2C%20and%20you%20drop%20coffee%20into%20the%20brewing%20tube%20so%20it%20rests%20on%20the%20filter.%20The%20AeroPress's%20packaging%20included%20a%20funnel%20for%20anyone%20concerned%20about%20spillage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20an%20AeroPress%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20an%20AeroPress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scooping%20coffee%20grounds%20into%20an%20AeroPress%20brewing%20tube.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65087efbcd637c0019c7168f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAeroPress%20recommends%20a%20grind%20that's%20halfway%20between%20the%20super-fine%20version%20used%20by%20espresso%20machines%20and%20the%20coarser%20texture%20required%20by%20drip%20coffee%20makers.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Tobin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20AeroPress%20comes%20with%20thorough%20instructions%20(also%20accessible%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faeropress.com%2Fpages%2Fhow-it-works%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCHAMPIONSHIP%2520RECIPES-%2CDetailed%2520instructions%2C-English%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20so%20you're%20ready%20to%20launch%20into%20brewing%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20open%20the%20box.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brewed%20espresso-style%20coffee%20by%20boiling%20water%20and%20allowing%20it%20to%20cool%20to%20the%20temperature%20recommended%20by%20AeroPress%2C%20175%20degrees%20F.%20I%20then%20poured%20just%20enough%20water%20to%20moisten%20the%20medium-fine%20grounds%20into%20the%20brewing%20tube%20and%20let%20it%20sit%20for%2030%20seconds%20to%20allow%20the%20coffee%20to%20%26quot%3Bbloom.%26quot%3B%20(A%20technique%20used%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-french-press%5C%22%3Ebest%20French%20press%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20add%20the%20ground%20coffee%20and%20water%20and%20stir%20to%20combine%2C%20you%20use%20the%20plunger%20to%20brew.%20I%20waited%2030%20seconds%20for%20the%20coffee%20to%20infuse%20the%20water.%20As%20you%20push%20down%20on%20the%20plunger%2C%20you%20add%20pressure%20to%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20brewing%20tube%2C%20which%20moves%20the%20water%20through%20the%20ground%20beans%20and%20extracts%20flavorful%20coffee%20in%20under%202%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20note%20on%20brewing%3A%20The%20AeroPress%20instructions%20call%20for%20a%20single%20scoop%20of%20coffee%20grounds%20per%20brew%20cycle.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20stronger%20brew%2C%20consider%20adding%20more%20coffee%20grounds%20to%20the%20brewing%20tube%2C%20stirring%20the%20water-coffee%20grounds%20mixture%20for%2010-15%20extra%20seconds%2C%20and%2For%20using%20dark-roast%20coffee%20(or%20espresso%20beans).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleanup%5C%22%3ECleanup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20of%20the%20AeroPress%20provides%20an%20easy%20cleanup%20process.%20I%20first%20unscrewed%20the%20filter%20basket%20from%20the%20brewing%20tube%20and%20used%20the%20plunger%20to%20push%20the%20filter%20and