%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20states%20which%20has%20never%20sent%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20to%20parliament.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20situation%20even%20after%202014%2C%20despite%20the%20state%20having%2055%20per%20cent%20voters%20belonging%20to%20the%20majority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20politics%20of%20the%20state%20has%20been%20bipolar%20for%20decades%2C%20swing%20between%20a%20Congress%20and%20a%20Left-led%20alliance.%20The%20state%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20few%20that%20routinely%20votes%20out%20the%20incumbent%20government.%20But%20in%202021%2C%20in%20a%20shocking%20break%20with%20tradition%2C%20Kerala%20gave%20a%20second%20term%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20state%20in%20its%20quest%20of%20370%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20was%20different%20this%20time%2C%20Anil%20Antony%20told%20NDTV%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20factors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20election%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20standing%20(from%20Wayanad)%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20narrative%20was%20created%20that%20the%20UPA%20was%20winning.%20The%20UPA%20would%20come%20back%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20would%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20There%20was%20some%20mood%20shift%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20votes%20in%20the%20assembly%20election%20was%20very%20different%20from%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20national%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bdire%20financial%20distress%26quot%3B%2C%20where%20the%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20pay%20salaries%20and%20pension%20to%20its%20employees.%20%26quot%3BSo%20from%20Kasaragod%20to%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20in%20each%20of%20the%2020%20seats%2C%20there%20is%20anti-incumbency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20you%20talk%20to%20a%20Congress%20or%20a%20CPM%20supporter%20and%20you%20will%20see%20the%20NDA-3%20is%20coming%20back%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C'%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Antony%20had%20quit%20the%20Congress%20and%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20last%20year.%20The%20party%20expects%20him%20to%20help%20expand%20its%20base%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20among%20Christians.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Antony%20Senior%20broke%20his%20silence%20over%20his%20son%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20Anil%20Antony%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20and%20will%20lose%20from%20Pathanamthitta%20and%20that%20it%20was%20wrong%20for%20children%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20had%20immediately%20joined%20issue.%20At%20an%20election%20rally%20for%20Anil%20Antony%2C%20he%20said%2C%20'%26quot%3BAll%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20Mr%20Antony%20is%3A%20even%20if%20he%20might%20not%20vote%20for%20him%2C%20he%20should%20bless%20him%20as%20a%20father.%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20what%20he%20said.%20Maybe%20he%20said%20so%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20the%20Congress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pathanamthitta%2C%20Mr%20Antony%20is%20up%20against%20Congress's%20Anto%20Antony%2C%20the%20three-time%20sitting%20MP%20and%20the%20Left's%20TM%20Thomas%20Issac%2C%20a%20former%20finance%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20candidature%20has%20upset%20senior%20politician%20PC%20George%2C%20who%20said%20fielding%20him%20has%20scuttled%20the%20BJP's%20chances%20in%20the%20constituency.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knows%20him.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20go%20around%20and%20introduce%20him%20to%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20senior%20leader%2C%20who%20recently%20merged%20his%20Kerala%20Janapaksham%20(Secular)%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714155540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F60hdb3fo_anil-antony_625x300_06_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-kerala-election-will-be-different-anil-antony-expresses-hope-for-bjp-in-kerala-5531787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anil%20Antony%2C%20the%20son%20of%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20AK%20Antony%20and%20the%20BJP's%20candidate%20from%20Pathanamthitta%2C%20insists%20the%20election%20this%20time%20in%20Kerala%20would%20be%20different.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-kerala-election-will-be-different-anil-antony-expresses-hope-for-bjp-in-kerala-5531787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-kerala-election-will-be-different-anil-antony-expresses-hope-for-bjp-in-kerala-5531787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-kerala-election-will-be-different-anil-antony-expresses-hope-for-bjp-in-kerala-5531787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20lays%20out%20norms%20for%20voluntary%20conversion%20of%20SFBs%20into%20universal%20banks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714155400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F26%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1714155333-0491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Frbi-lays-out-norms-for-voluntary-conversion-of-sfbs-into-universal-banks-124042601343_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AU%20SFB%2C%20a%20few%20others%20seen%20as%20contenders%20for%20conversion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Frbi-lays-out-norms-for-voluntary-conversion-of-sfbs-