%20Awardee%20Paramilitary%20Officer%20Guilty%20Of%20Sex%20Abuse%2C%20Faces%20Dismissal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20high-ranking%20officer%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20has%20been%20served%20notice%20for%20dismissal%20from%20service%20after%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20sex%20harassment%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhajan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20(DIG)%20rank%20chief%20sports%20officer%20of%20the%20CRPF%2C%20sexually%20harassed%20women%20personnel%20in%20the%20paramilitary%20force%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20allegations%20by%20the%20women%2C%20the%20CRPF%20investigated%20the%20matter%20and%20found%20him%20guilty.%20The%20country's%20largest%20paramilitary%20force%20then%20gave%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%2C%20which%20asked%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20to%20dismiss%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20enquiry%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20CRPF%20against%20the%20officer.%20Following%20due%20process%20of%20law%2C%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20and%20a%20report%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20UPSC.%20Now%2C%20the%20UPSC%20recommended%20his%20dismissal.%20The%20MHA%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20has%20also%20approved%20it.%20The%20CRPF%20has%20issued%20dismissal%20notice%20to%20the%20officer%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20CRPF%20chief%20sports%20officer%2C%20he%20had%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%201986%20Seoul%20Asian%20Games%20in%20the%20200%20metres%20butterfly%20event%2C%20which%20was%20India's%20first%20medal%20in%20swimming%20at%20the%20event%20since%201951.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhajan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20posted%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20has%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20yet.%20He%20has%20been%20given%2015%20days%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20dismissal%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faces%20two%20charges%20and%20the%20notice%20for%20dis