20stopped%20due%20to%20the%20non-formation%20of%20its%20standing%20committee.%20The%20matter%20concerning%20the%20non-formation%20of%20standing%20committee%2C%20the%20highest%20decision-making%20body%20of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%2C%20was%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20AAP%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20LG%20illegally%20appointed%20aldermen%20(nominated%20councillors).%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20standing%20committee%20could%20not%20be%20formed.%20The%20LG%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20non-formation%20of%20the%20standing%20committee%20due%20to%20which%20the%20work%20of%20the%20MCD%20was%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20alleged%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observations%20came%20after%20the%20Delhi%20government%20counsel%20said%20the%20matter%20requires%20certain%20approvals%20from%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20who%20is%20in%20custody%20in%20the%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202021%20excise%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stated%20that%20till%20now%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bpolitely%26quot%3B%20emphasised%20that%20national%20interest%20is%20%26quot%3Bsupreme%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20present%20case%20has%20highlighted%20what%20was%20%26quot%3Bwrong%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20would%20pass%20an%20order%20in%20the%20matter%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20sorry%20to%20say%20you%20have%20placed%20your%20interest%20above%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20students%2C%20the%20children%20that%20are%20studying.%20That%20is%20very%20clear%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20give%20that%20finding%20that%20you%20have%20placed%20your%20political%20interest%20at%20a%20higher%20pedestal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20you%20have%20done%20this.%20It%20is%20wrong%20and%20that%20is%20what%20has%20got%20highlighted%20in%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20Manmohan%20and%20Justice%20Manmeet%20P%20S%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20told%20the%20Delhi%20government%20lawyer%20that%20his%20client%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20interested%20in%20appropriation%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20power%20you%20want.%20The%20problem%20is%20because%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20appropriate%20power%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20are%20not%20getting%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20personal%20call%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20wants%20the%20administration%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bparalysed%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20further%20said%20the%20persons%20who%20lead%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bcarry%20everyone%20along%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20cannot%20be%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bone%20man%20upmanship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20counsel%20said%20he%20was%20not%20appearing%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20non-supply%20of%20educational%20material%20would%20be%20resolved%20if%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20commissioner%20makes%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20financial%20approvals%20even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20civic%20body's%20standing%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20counsel%20was%20appearing%20on%20instructions%20from%20the%20Urban%20Development%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20and%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20record%20your%20statement%20that%20it%20is%20because%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20in%20custody%20that%20I%20cannot%20do%20anything.%20If%20that's%20his%20personal%20call%2C%20good%20luck%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BChoice%20is%20yours%20that%20the%20chief%20minster%20will%20continue%20despite%20being%20in%20jail.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20say%20this.%20This%20is%20your%20administration's%20will.%20You%20are%20asking%20us%20to%20go%20down%20that%20track%20and%20we%20will%20come%20with%20full%20vigour%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Manmohan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20PIL%20by%20NGO%20Social%20Jurist%2C%20represented%20by%20advocate%20Ashok%20Agarwal%2C%20highlighting%20the%20non-supply%20of%20educational%20material%20and%20other%20statutory%20benefits%20to%20students%20in%20the%20MCD%20schools%20even%20after%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20new%20academic%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCD%20commissioner%20had%20earlier%20stated%20that%20the%20non-distribution%20of%20the%20facilities%20was%20due%20to%20the%20non-formation%20of%20a%20standing%20committee%20which%20has%20the%20power%20to%20reward%20contracts%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20then%20prima%20facie%20said%20there%20could%20not%20be%20a%20vacuum%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20standing%20committee%20and%20in%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20financial%20power%20has%20to%20be%20delegated%20forthwith%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20another%20appropriate%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20counsel%20said%20the%20MCD%20commissioner%20was%20free%20to%20seek%20the%20necessary%20financial%20approvals%20even%20in%20such%20situations%20and%20an%20appropriate%20resolution%20would%20be%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20people%20can't%20even%20elect%20your%20committee%20and%20you%20are%20telling%20us%20you%20will%20pass%20the%20resolution%3F...%20Do%20you%20want%20us%20to%20take%20judicial%20notice%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20house%3F%20How%20the%20people%20are%20pushing%20each%20other%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20remarked%20that%20several%20projects%20concerning%20distribution%20of%20books%20and%20medicines%20were%20admittedly%20stalled%2C%20and%20questioned%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20you%20have%20a%20heart%3F%20Don't%20you%20feel%20for%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20are%20seeing%20any%20of%20this.%20I%20think%20you%20are%20just%20shedding%20crocodile%20tears%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20does%20not%20feel%20for%20the%20common%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDesks%20and%20chairs%20are%20broken..%20Would%20any%20of%20the%20corporators%20like%20their%20children%20to%20study%20in%20that%20manner%3F%20Will%20the%20mayor%20like%20her%20children%20to%20study%20in%20a%20place%20where%20tables%20are%20broken%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714154100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdont-know-how-much-power-you-want-delhi-high-court-raps-delhi-government-5530816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20pulled%20up%20the%20city%20government%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20non-supply%20of%20books%20to%20the%20children%20studying%20in%20MCD%20schools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdont-know-how-much-power-you-want-delhi-high-court-raps-delhi-government-5530816%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdont-know-how-much-power-you-want-delhi-high-court-raps-delhi-government-5530816%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdont-know-how-much-power-you-want-delhi-high-court-raps-delhi-government-5530816%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nearly%20Half%20Of%20Bengaluru%20Voters%20Skip%20Voting%20In%20Phas