ncrease%20turnout%20in%20this%20election%20in%20urban%20constituencies%20--%20from%20encouraging%20the%20public%20to%20use%20various%20apps%20to%20putting%20QR%20codes%20on%20voter%20slips%20to%20locate%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoter%20Helpline%2C%20'Know%20Your%20Candidate'%20and%20updating%20details%20about%20number%20of%20voters%20in%20queue%20and%20kind%20of%20parking%20facilities%20available%20at%20polling%20booths%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20an%20elaborate%20booth%20election%20management%20plan%20were%20among%20the%20other%20measures%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20had%20also%20come%20up%20with%20better%20facilities%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20in%20the%20urban%20constituencies%20based%20on%20the%20feedback%20they%20received%20following%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20the%20areas%20which%20registered%20low%20voter%20turnout%20in%20the%202023%20Karnataka%20Assembly%20election%20and%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714154040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5gtls1cg_bengaluru-voters-lok-sabha-polls-2024_625x300_26_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fnearly-half-of-bengaluru-voters-skip-voting-in-phase-2-of-lok-sabha-polls-2024-5531657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20half%20of%20Bengaluru's%20voters%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20Friday.%20Voting%20took%20place%20in%2014%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20estimating%20the%20turnout%20at%2069.23%20per%20cent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fnearly-h