ic%20films%20like%20'Deewaar'%20and%20'Kabhi%20Kabhie%2C'%20Kapoor%20felt%20he%20hadn't%20met%20the%20award's%20standards.%20His%20humility%20didn't%20hinder%20later%20successes%2C%20including%20multiple%20National%20Awards%20and%20prestigious%20honors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshashi-kapoors-humility-declining-national-award-due-to-perceived-incompetence%2Farticleshow%2F109630800.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20PM%20Modi's%20High-Octane%20Bengal%20Rally%2C%20Trinamool's%20%26quot%3BFact-Check%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20high-octane%20election%20campaign%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20published%20a%20list%20of%20comments%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20and%20%26quot%3Bfact-checked%26quot%3B%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETearing%20into%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20erstwhile%20Left%20Front%20government%20in%20the%20state%20for%20putting%20brakes%20on%20development%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20they%20wrecked%20the%20greatness%2C%20global%20image%20and%20the%20dignity%20of%20Bengal%20under%20their%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party%20is%20under%20the%20spotlight%20again%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20appointments%20for%20teaching%20posts%20after%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20recently%20cancelled%20over%2025%2C000%20recruitments%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Bengal%20was%20the%20engine%20of%20the%20country's%20development%20and%20progress.%20Be%20it%20social%20reforms%2C%20scientific%20advancements%2C%20as%20well%20as%20philosophical%20and%20spiritual%20thinking%20and%20awakening%2C%20Bengal%20led%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Malda%20district%2C%20where%20the%20majority%20of%20voters%20are%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20Left%20Front%20and%20the%20present%20TMC%20regime%20robbed%20Bengal%20of%20its%20greatness%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20and%20lowered%20its%20dignity%20and%20prestige%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world.%20Only%20scams%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20are%20flourishing%20in%20Bengal%20under%20TMC%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20brick%20is%20laid%20in%20Bengal%20without%20money%20changing%20hands.%20Corruption%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20the%20state.%20They%20(TMC)%20did%20not%20even%20spare%20farmers.%20They%20played%20with%20the%20future%20of%20the%20state's%20youth%20and%20have%20now%20left%2026%2C000%20families%20jobless.%20They%20are%20facing%20the%20burden%20of%20unpaid%20loans%20that%20they%20took%20to%20pay%20the%20TMC%20in%20exchange%20for%20these%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrinamool's%20%26quot%3BFact-Check%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20said%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20withheld%20funds%20worth%20Rs%201.6%20lakh%20crore%20under%20various%20heads%20for%20Bengal.%20This%20was%20in%20response%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20comment%20that%20only%20the%20BJP%20is%20working%20for%20Bengal's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20PM%20Modi's%20comment%20that%20the%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%20and%20the%20Start%20Up%20India%20programme%20have%20empowered%20the%20youth%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20claimed%20the%20placement%20rate%20for%20the%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%202.0%20stood%20at%2023%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20for%20the%20PMKVY%203.0%2C%20it%20was%20even%20lower%20at%208%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20said%20in%20the%20rally%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20had%20not%20been%20allowing%20the%20Centre%20to%20start%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%2040%20per%20cent%20funds%20under%20this%20scheme%20should%20come%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBengal%20has%20a%20better%20health%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20Swasthya%20Sathi.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20cover%2C%20entire%20amount%20bourne%20by%20the%20state.%20Completely%20paperless%2C%20cashless%2C%20parents%20of%20both%20spouses%20covered%20and%20free%20treatment%20for%20all%20in%20government%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20slammed%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20over%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20The%20Trinamool%20shot%20back%2C%20saying%20the%20Bengal%20police%20arrested%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20accused%20in%2072%20hours.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20took%20no%20action%20against%20a%20BJP%20MP%20who%20sexually%20assaulted%20champion%20women%20wrestlers...%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714143480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8gdquk9o_mamata-modi-split-650_625x300_12_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-pm-narendra-modis-high-octane-bengal-rally-trinamools-fact-check-5530540%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20high-octane%20election%20campaign%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20published%20a%20list%20of%20comments%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20and%20%26quot%3Bfact-checked%26quot%3B%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-pm-narendra-modis-high-octane-bengal-rally-trinamools-fact-check-5530540%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-pm-narendra-modis-high-octane-bengal-rally-trinamools-fact-check-55