ustice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20judges%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20got%20a%20judicial%20seal%20of%20approval%20on%20the%20sanctity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20EVM%20system%20of%20conducting%20elections.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20repetition%20of%20the%20past%2C%20it%20has%20already%20happened%20before.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20court%20had%20already%20been%20through%20and%20given%20it%20their%20endorsement.%20So%20these%20are%20all%20motivated%20litigations.%20As%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20pointed%20out%20this%20time%2C%20it%20was%20based%20only%20on%20suspicion.%20There%20were%20no%20hard%20facts%20to%20invoke%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20motivated%20petition%2C%20it%20is%20really%20done%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20who%20are%20not%20so%20much%20concerned%20about%20strengthening%20our%20electoral%20process%2C%20but%20casting%20a%20doubt%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20our%20democratic%20processes...%20In%20my%20view%2C%20this%20is%20an%20extremely%20anti-national%20step%20to%20keep%20casting%20doubt%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20process.%20Because%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20undermine%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20government%20you%20don't%20agree%20with.%20You%20are%20a%20bad%20loser%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20thundered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethmalani%20said%20since%20the%20issue%20was%20serious%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20spent%20some%20time%20on%20it%20and%20gave%20the%20electoral%20process%20another%20seal%20of%20approval.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20call%20them%20a%20mob%20that%20moves%20these%20petitions.%20Their%20intent%20is%20always%20questionable%20and%20they%20are%20really%20badly%20motivated%20rabble-rousers.%20There%20is%20no%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20in%20the%20actions%20they%20take%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20really%20sober%20institution%20like%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20And%20they%20make%20the%20world%20watch.%20You%20can%20go%20and%20give%20press%20conferences.%20It's%20self-publicity%20and%20it%20is%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20nation's%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Partisan%20Petition'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20two%20new%20safeguards%20put%20in%20place%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20sealing%20and%20storing%20the%20symbol%20loading%20unit%20for%20at%20least%2045%20days%20and%20allowing%20checking%20the%20burnt%20memory%20in%20the%20EVM%20microcontroller%20if%20candidates%20request%20for%20it%20-%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20it%2C%20but%20added%20that%20it%20is%20good%20that%20these%20extra%20precautions%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20now%20show%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20only%20examined%20the%20issue%20yet%20another%20time%2C%20but%20examined%20it%20to%20the%20point%20of%20such%20care%20that%20they%20don't%20want%20any%20future%20reopening%20of%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMounting%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20opposition%20and%20Senior%20Advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20never%20questions%20EVMs%20when%20parties%20opposing%20them%20win%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20motives%20of%20someone%20like%20Prashant%20Bhushan.%20When%20the%20opposition%20wins%20in%20Karnataka%20or%20the%20Left%20wins%20in%20Kerala%2C%20then%20the%20EVMs%20are%20sacrosanct.%20That's%20how%20partisan%20this%20is.%20This%20is%20motivated%20not%20only%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20undermining%20BJP%20victories%20and%20India's%20electoral%20process%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20cabal%20that%20operates%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20opposition.%20I'm%20saying%20that%20very%20clearly%2C%20and%20I%20can%20prove%20it.%20Every%20time%20this%20group%20has%20done%20it...%20it%20has%20never%20championed%20causes%20where%20the%20opposition%20is%20covered%20in%20mud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20LK%20Advani%20and%20Subramanian%20Swami%20having%20raised%20doubts%20on%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20recall%20Mr%20Advani%20ever%20taking%20this%20issue%20up.%20What%20can%20one%20say%20about%20Dr%20Subramanian%20Swami%3F%20He's%20a%20busybody%20in%20court.%20He%20goes%20and%20he%20takes%20up%20all%20kinds%20of%20issues.%20Dr%20Swamy%20doesn't%20repeat%20the%20same%20issue%20over%20and%20over.%20And%20nobody%20can%20accuse%20Dr%20Swamy%20of%20being%20partisan.%20He's%20a%20maverick%20%C2%A0politician%2C%20his%20guns%20can%20be%20trained%20on%20anybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethmalani%20also%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20uses%20these%20petitioners%20as%20a%20front%20because%20it%20would%2C%20otherwise%2C%20have%20to%20answer%20why%20it%20does%20not%20complain%20about%20EVMs%20when%20it%20wins.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714140300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F312efh8g_mahesh-jethmalani_625x300_26_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-moves-these-petitions-mahesh-jetmalani-on-verdict-in-vvpat-case-5530198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alleging%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcabal%26quot%3B%20operating%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20senior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20has%20termed%20the%20VVPAT%20verification%20petition%20motivated%20and%20said%20the%20intention%20was%20to%20cast%20a%20doubt%20on%20the%20sancity%20of%20India's%20electoral%20processes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-moves-these-petitions-mahesh-jetmalani-on-verdict-in-vvpat-case-5530198%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-moves-these-petitions-mahesh-jetmalani-on-verdict-in-vvpat-case-5530198%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-moves-these-petitions-mahesh-jetmalani-on-verdict-in-vvpat-case-5530198%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEffort%20To%20Discredit%20India's%20Progress%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Raps%20VVPAT%20Petitioners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20in%20the%20EVM%20case%2C%20the%20non-profit%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20or%20ADR%2C%20got%20a%20stern%20warning%20today%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20said%20%26quot%3Bblindly%20doubting%20a%20system%20can%20breed%20scepticism%26quot%3B.%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20said%2C%20''I%20have%20serious%20doubt%20as%20regards%20the%20bona%20fides%20of%20the%20petitioning%20association%20when%20it%20seeks%20a%20reversion%20to%20the%20old%20order%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIrrespective%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20past%20efforts%20of%20the%20petitioning%20association%20in%20bringing%20about%20electoral%20reforms%20have%20borne%20fruit%2C%20the%20suggestion%20put%20forth%20appeared%20inexplicable%2C'%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20there%20has%20been%20a%20rise%20of%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20vested%20interest%20groups%26quot%3B%20that%20try%20to%20undermine%20the%20achievements%20and%20accomplishments%20of%20the%20nation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20discredit%2C%20diminish%2C%20and%20weaken%20the%20progress%20of%20this%20great%20nation%20on%20every%20possible%20frontier.%20Any%20such%20effort%2C%20or%20rather%20attempt%2C%20has%20to%20be%20nipped%20in%20the%20bud%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20rejected%20the%20petitioner's%20demand%20that%20all%20votes%20cast%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20be%20verified%20through%20paper%20slips%20generated%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20(Voter-Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail)%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20balanced%20perspective%20is%20important%2C%20blindly%20doubting%20a%20system%20can%20breed%20scepticism%20and%20thus%2C%20meaningful%20criticism%20is%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20and%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20had%20said%20while%20delivering%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADR%20petition%20was%20one%20of%20several%20that%20sought%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%2C%20citing%20discrepancy%20with%20data%20uploaded%20on%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20machines%20leave%20room%20for%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20had%20also%20sought%20a%20return%20to%20ballot%20papers%2C%20citing%20the%20example%20of%20several%20other%20nations%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20Germany%20and%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20where%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%20is%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20in%20a%20vast%20and%20populous%20country%20like%20India%2C%20EVMs%20streamline%20the%20voting%20process%20and%20reduces%20the%20chances%20of%20rigging%20and%20mis-count%20of%20votes%20that%20are%20high%20in%20a%20ballot-paper%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20draw%20analogies%20and%20comparisons%20from%20Germany%20and%20other%20countries.%20My%20home%20state%20West%20Bengal%20has%20more%20population%20than%20what%20Mr%20Bhushan%20(Prashant%20Bhushan%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20ADR)%20said%20about%20Germany's%20population.%20It's%20a%20very%20small%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20out%20the%20lack%20of%20data%20in%20the%20ADR%20petition%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20rational%20scepticism%20of%20the%20status%20quo%20is%20desirable%20in%20a%20healthy%20democracy%2C%20this%20Court%20cannot%20allow%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20the%20underway%20General%20Elections%20to%20be%20called%20into%20question%20and%20upended%20on%20mere%20apprehension%20and%20speculation%20of%20the%20petitioners%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714140180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgeja10k4_evm-generic-voring-machine-generic-ani_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-evm-vvpat-supreme-court-raises-doubts-about-petitioners-bonafides-in-evm-case-5529884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20petitioner%20in%20the%20EVM%20case%2C%20the%20non-profit%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20or%20ADR%2C%20got%20a%20stern%20warning%20today%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20said%20%26quot%3Bblindly%20doubting%20a%20system%20can%20breed%20scepticism%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-evm-vvpat-supreme-court-raises-doubts-about-petitioners-bonafides-in-evm-case-5529884%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-evm-vvpat-supreme-court-raises-doubts-about-petitioners-bonafides-in-evm-case-5529884%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-evm-vvpat-supreme-court-raises-doubts-about-petitioners-bonafides-in-evm-case-5529884%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMatter%20Of%20Pride%20That%20PM%20Modi...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shami%20After%20Casting%20Vote%20In%20Amroha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20star%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami%20on%20Friday%20cast%20his%20vote%20in%20Amroha%20during%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20After%20casting%20his%20vote%2C%20Shami%20urged%20citizens%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20and%20%26quot%3Belect%20the%20government%20of%20their%20choice%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20to%20say%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20the%20right%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%20and%20elect%20the%20government%20of%20their%20choice...It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20me%20that%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20my%20name%20during%20his%20speech%20(in%20Amroha)%20and%20praised%20me%20and%20my%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20told%20the%20media.%20Voting%20was%20held%20in%20eight%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20Amroha%2C%20Meerut%2C%20Baghpat%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Gautam%20Budh%20Nagar%2C%20Aligarh%2C%20Mathura%2C%20and%20Bulandshahr%20during%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20began%20at%207%20am%20on%20Friday%20in%2088%20constituencies%20across%2013%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20for%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20PM%20Modi%20wished%20a%20speedy%20recovery%20to%20Shami%2C%20who%20successfully%20underwent%20an%20operation%20on%20his%20Achilles%20tendon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20is%20currently%20in%20rehabilitation%20from%20an%20Achilles%20tendon%20injury.%20On%20April%2019%2C%20Shami%20provided%20his%20fans%20with%20an%20injury%20update%20and%20said%20that%20he%20cannot%20wait%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20Instagram%2C%20Shami%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20of%20his%20reel%2C%20%26quot%3BInjuries%20don't%20define%20you%2C%20your%20comeback%20will...%20Can't%20wait%20to%20be%20back%20out%20there%20with%20my%20team!%20%23mdshami%20%23recoveryjourney%20%23shami%20%23mdshami11%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20is%20not%20playing%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20season%2C%20where%20he%20was%20supposed%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20and%20also%20missed%20the%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20England%20at%20home%20in%20January-March%20this%20year%20due%20to%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20last%20represented%20India%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia%20in%20November.%20The%20senior%20pacer%20finished%20as%20the%20tournament's%20highest%20wicket-taker%20and%20took%2024%20wickets%20in%20only%20seven%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20played%20through%20pain%20in%20that%20tournament%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20allow%20his%20pain%20to%20affect%20his%20performance.%20He%20later%20missed%20the%20tour%20to%20South%20Africa%20following%20the%20tournament%20and%20the%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714140180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fbd1os3bo_mohammed-shami-instagram_625x300_26_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmatter-of-pride-that-pm-modi-took-my-name-india-pacer-mohammed-shami-after-casting-his-vote-in-uttar-pradeshs-amroha-5529761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20star%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami%20on%20Friday%20cast%20his%20vote%20in%20Amroha%20during%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Hits%20Rs%2041%20Lakh%20Jackpot%20After%20Boyfriend's%20Lottery%20Ticket%20Advice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20from%20Maryland%20is%20celebrating%20a%20%2450%2C000%20(Rs%2041%2C66977)%20Powerball%20win%20after%20her%20boyfriend%20convinced%20her%20to%20buy%20a%20lottery%20ticket.%20The%20lucky%20winner%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BOlney%20Winner%26quot%3B%20after%20her%20Maryland%20locality%2C%20purchased%20a%20%2410%20quick-pick%20ticket%20at%20Weis%20Markets%20in%20Laurel%20before%20the%20April%2020th%20drawing.%20The%20ticket%20remained%20forgotten%20in%20her%20purse%20until%20Monday%2C%20when%20she%20discovered%20it%20and%20scanned%20it%20using%20the%20Maryland%20Lottery%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20release%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdlottery.com%2Fbowie-womans-store-run-leads-to-50000-win%2F%5C%22%3EMaryland%20lottery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20headed%20home%20and%20scratched%20off%20her%20instant%20tickets.%20Bren%20checked%20her%20ticket%20on%20the%20Maryland%20Lottery%20app%20a%20few%20times%2C%20and%20it%20confirmed%20what%20she%20thought-a%20top%20prize%20win%20worth%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20screamed%20because%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20shouted%20so%20loudly%20that%20I%20thought%20my%20neighbours%20could%20hear%20me.%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20because%20you%20never%20expect%20to%20win.%20I%20really%20just%20play%20for%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Bren%20Bren%20isn't%20sure%20how%20she%20will%20spend%20her%20money%2C%20she%20intends%20to%20invest%20more%20in%20her%20business%20by%20purchasing%20another%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20role%20in%20selling%20the%20%2450%2C000%20top%20prize-winning%20scratch-off%2C%20Landover%20Hills%20Exxon%20at%206579%20Annapolis%20Road%20also%20wins.%20The%20Prince%20Georges%20County%20gas%20station%20will%20receive%20a%20%24500%20bonus%20from%20the%20lottery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20only%20instance%20in%20the%20US%20where%20someone%20has%20won%20a%20huge%20amount.%20Last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmystery-person-in-us-wins-1-13-billion-jackpot-8th-largest-in-us-history-5321195%5C%22%3Ea%20mystery%20person%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20New%20Jersey%3C%2Fa%3E%20won%20a%20whopping%20%241.13%20billion%20Mega%20Millions%20jackpot.%20Lottery%20officials%20announced%20that%20a%20single%20ticket%20matched%20all%20six%20numbers%20drawn.%20It%20was%20the%20fifth-largest%20prize%20ever%20won%20by%20Mega%20Millions%20players%2C%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year%2C%20a%20ticket%20matched%20all%20the%20numbers%20needed%20to%20get%20the%20grand%20prize.%20The%20estimated%20jackpot%20was%20also%20the%20eighth-largest%20in%20US%20lottery%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714140180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3udsv1do_maryland-lottery_625x300_26_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fus-woman-hits-rs-41-lakh-jackpot-after-boyfriends-lottery-ticket-advice-5530189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20told%20Lottery%20officials%20that%20scratching%20her%20ticket%20and%20seeing%20the%20%2450%2C000%20prize%20was%20something%20she%20could%20have%20never%20have%20imagined.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fus-woman-hits-rs-41-lakh-jackpot-after-boyfriends-lottery-ticket-advice-5530189%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fus-woman-hits-rs-41-lakh-jackpot-after-boyfriends-lottery-ticket-advice-5530189%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fus-woman-hits-rs-41-lakh-jackpot-after-boyfriends-lottery-ticket-advice-5530189%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SBI%20Card%20Q4%20results%3A%20PAT%20rises%2011%25%20to%20Rs%20662%20cr%2C%20total%20revenue%20rises%2014%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714140139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1683040378-1953