ad-said-on-evms-5526933%5C%22%3EElectronic%20Voting%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%20(EVMs).%20The%20voting%20machine%20has%20always%20been%20mired%20in%20controversies%2C%20with%20debates%20heating%20up%20around%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-vvpat-lok-sabha-election-2024-as-india-votes-today-a-look-at-how-evm-and-vvpat-polling-machines-work-5474620%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20repeatedly%20defended%20EVMs%20as%20non-tamperable%2C%20citing%20technological%20measures%20and%20strict%20administrative%20and%20security%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvvpat-evm-case-supreme-court-verdict-in-vvpat-case-supreme-courts-2-big-directions-on-evms-symbol-units-5526842%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0In%20VVPAT%20Case%2C%20Supreme%20Court's%202%20Big%20Directions%20On%20EVMs%2C%20Symbol%20Units%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20S.%20Rangarajan%2C%20the%20man%20who%20designed%20the%20EVM%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20here%20to%20defend%20the%20device%20that%20has%20drastically%20reduced%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20count%20votes.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20more%20popularly%20known%20as%20'writer%20Sujatha'%20-%20among%20the%20most%20prolific%20writers%20in%20Tamil%20-%20who%20wrote%20thrillers%2C%20science%20fiction%2C%20human%20drama%2C%20critiques%20on%20Tamil%20classics%2C%20and%20explained%20science%20and%20technology.%20He%20also%20wrote%20screenplays%20that%20went%20on%20to%20become%20hugely%20successful.%20If%20alive%2C%20he%20would%20have%20turned%2089%20on%20May%203%20this%20year.%20He%20passed%20away%20on%20February%2027%2C%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20History%20Of%20The%20Machine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERangarajan%20was%20an%20electronic%20engineer%20at%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20(BEL)%2C%20where%20he%20led%20the%20team%20that%20designed%20such%20machines.%20After%20their%20experimental%20use%20in%201989%2C%20followed%20by%20other%20successful%20exercises%20during%20elections%2C%20about%20one%20million%20EVMs%20were%20deployed%20in%20the%202004%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201977%2C%20S.L.%20Shakdhar%2C%20the%20then%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%2C%20during%20a%20tour%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20requested%20the%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20(ECIL)%20to%20study%20the%20possibility%20of%20using%20an%20electronic%20device%20for%20conducting%20elections%2C%20writes%20Anil%20Maheshwari%20and%20Vipul%20Maheshwari%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Power%20of%20the%20Ballot%3A%20Travail%20and%20Triumph%20in%20the%20Elections%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%201979%2C%20a%20prototype%20was%20developed%2C%20and%20its%20operation%20was%20demonstrated%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20before%20the%20representatives%20of%20political%20parties%20in%20August%201980%2C%20they%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-opposition-dreams-shattered-says-pm-on-evm-vvpat-congress-responds-5528937%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BOpposition's%20Dreams%20Shattered%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20VVPAT%20Verdict.%20Congress%20Responds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BEL%2C%20a%20Defence%20Ministry%20PSU%2C%20had%20also%20developed%20a%20microcomputer-based%20voting%20equipment%2C%20which%20they%20had%20used%20for%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20various%20unions%20of%20the%20company%2C%20say%20the%20authors.%20In%20January%201981%2C%20BEL%20approached%20the%20ECI%20for%20a%20contract%20for%20manufacturing%20EVMs%2C%20and%20on%20July%2029%2C%201981%2C%20the%20ECI%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20representatives%20of%20BEL%2C%20ECIL%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%2C%20and%20the%20CEOs%20of%20some%20states%20regarding%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20VVPAT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20its%20introduction%2C%20some%20parties%20have%20raised%20doubts%20over%20the%20possibility%20of%20EVMs%20malfunctioning%20or%20being%20tampered%20with%20to%20register%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20particular%20candidate%20or%20party.%20Even%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-all-petitions-seeking-100-verification-of-vvpat-slips-during-elections-5526314%5C%22%3EVoter-Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20satisfy%20complainers.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIncidentally%2C%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20attached%20to%20the%20main%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-cant-control-elections-supreme-court-during-vvpat-case-hearing-5512115%5C%22%3EEVM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20button%20is%20pressed%2C%20prints%20out%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20with%20the%20voter's%20choice.%20The%20printed%20slip%20is%20visible%20for%20seven%20seconds.%20These%20slips%20are%20used%20later%20by%20officials%20to%20verify%20the%20votes%20cast%20in%20randomly%20selected%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20introducing%20more%20transparency%20into%20the%20election%20process%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20VVPAT%20was%20proposed%20in%202010.%20Following%20discussions%20with%20political%20parties%20and%20others%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20ECI's%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee.%20Finally%2C%20VVPAT%20machines%20were%20attached%20to%20EVMs%20and%20trials%20were%20conducted%20in%20some%20constituencies%20during%20the%202013%20assembly%20elections.%20Following%20that%2C%20the%20ECI%20decided%20to%20introduce%20VVPATs%20in%20a%20phased%20manner%2C%20and%20in%20the%202019%20General%20Elections%2C%20all%20EVMs%20were%20used%20with%20VVPAT%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Ex-Poll%20Commissioners%20Have%20Said%20About%20EVMs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20point%20out%20two%20things.%20Firstly%2C%20it%20was%20precisely%20to%20remove%20doubts%20regarding%20the%20EVMs%20that%20VVPAT%20machines%20were%20introduced%20-%20to%20provide%20voters%20with%20a%20means%20to%20verify%20that%20their%20vote%20was%20cast%20correctly%20and%20for%20the%20audit%20of%20stored%20electronic%20results.%20Using%20these%20machines%2C%20voters%20can%20review%20a%20physical%20ballot%20to%20confirm%20their%20electronic%20vote.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20was%20the%20VVPAT%20machines%20that%20malfunctioned%20in%20the%20recent%20by-polls%2C%20and%20not%20the%20EVMs%2C%26quot%3B%20writes%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20S.Y.%20Quraishi%20in%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EIndia's%20Experiment%20With%20Democracy%3A%20The%20Life%20of%20a%20Nation%20Through%20Its%20Elections%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chronology%20of%20events%20-%20from%20the%20seed%20of%20an%20idea%20to%20its%20development%20to%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20EVMs%20-%20shows%20that%20the%20process%20progressed%20through%20several%20Union%20governments.%20Yet%2C%20the%20same%20leaders%20who%20may%20have%20raised%20objections%20over%20polling%20through%20EVMs%20have%20been%20content%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%20has%20observed%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20'tamperability'%20of%20EVMs%20has%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20ever%20since%20they%20were%20first%20introduced.%20Every%20time%20a%20political%20party%20loses%20an%20election%2C%20it%20blames%20the%20machine.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20them%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prove%20their%20allegations%20against%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%2C%20and%20neither%20do%20they%20apologise%20when%20they%20win%20the%20elections%20where%20the%20same%20EVMs%20have%20been%20used.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERangarajan's%20Defence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrong%20words%20indeed.%20Doubts%2C%20then%20aspersions%2C%20were%20directed%20at%20EVMs%20-%20over%20their%20accuracy%20and%20security%20-%20since%20these%20were%20used%20experimentally.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Rangarajan%20took%20to%20writing%20in%20defence%20of%20his%20creation%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20machines%20being%20secure%20and%20tamper-proof.%20He%20had%20even%20been%20quoted%20saying%20that%20EVM%20was%20one%20invention%20that%20made%20him%20as%20proud%20as%20did%20his%20writings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20just%20a%20year%20after%20his%20demise%2C%20EVMs%20were%20back%20in%20the%20news%2C%20again%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20Former%20CEC%20Navin%20Chawla%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EEvery%20Vote%20Counts%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20India's%20Elections%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20remembers%20from%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20EVM%20continues%20to%20be%20buffeted%20in%20stormy%20seas.%20A%20concerted%20attack%20emerged%20in%202009...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20next%20year%2C%20Hari%20Prasad%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20American%20computer%20scientist%20J.%20Alex%20Halderman%20and%20Dutch%20hacker%20Rop%20Gonggrijp%2C%20claimed%20to%20have%20shown%20ways%20of%20tampering%20with%20EVMs.%20However%2C%20Prasad%20was%20unable%20to%20justify%20how%20he%20was%20able%20to%20acquire%20a%20real%20EVM.%20He%20was%20subsequently%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20theft%20of%20the%20machine%20allegedly%20from%20a%20customs%20house%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20it%20was%20stored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20about%20two%20dozen%20countries%20have%20EVMs%20or%20a%20similar%20system%20of%20voting%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20its%20views%20on%20%26quot%3BEVM%20detractors%26quot%3B%2C%20posted%20on%20its%20website%3A%20%26quot%3BSelf-appointed%20technical%20experts%20and%20certain%20social%20media%20personnel%20have%20repeatedly%20failed%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20compared%20to%20a%20computer%2C%20which%20runs%20on%20an%20operating%20system.%20The%20microcontrollers%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20run%20on%20a%20specific%20program%20designed%20to%20faithfully%20record%20the%20voters'%20choice.%20That%20the%20EVM%20is%20a%20truthful%20machine%20has%20been%20proved%20over%20decades%20of%20usage%20through%20changes%20in%20several%20governments%20at%20the%20state%20and%20central%20level%2C%20whenever%20the%20public%20wanted%20to.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20EVM%20has%20made%20elections%20safe%20and%20virtually%20eradicated%20booth%20capturing%20by%20limiting%20the%20rate%20of%20vote%20casting%20to%20four%20votes%20a%20minute%20and%20thus%20significantly%20increasing%20the%20time%20required%20for%20stuffing%20false%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jayanta%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%C2%A0writing%20on%20polls%20and%20politics%2C%20conflict%2C%20farmer%20and%20human%20interest%20issues)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714135140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Faq7kpjgc_evm-generic_625x300_21_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-evms-have-evolved-despite-controversies-5529019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20(EVM)%20has%20always%20been%20mired%20in%20controversies-with%20debates%20heating%20up%20around%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%20Unfortunately%2C%20S.%20Rangarajan%2C%20the%20man%20who%20designed%20the%20EVM%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20here%20to%20defend%20the%20device.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-evms-have-evolved-despite-controversies-5529019%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CRED%20to%20roll%20out%20payment%20checkout%20terminals%2