0over%2015%20hours%20in%20the%20boat%2C%20they%20started%20their%20swim%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20motivated%20by%20their%20crew%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Navy.%20The%2032%20km%20swim%20was%20conducted%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20experts%2C%20who%20helped%20the%20swimmers%20navigate%20and%20provided%20nutrition%20during%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20to%20success%20and%20the%20road%20to%20failure%20are%20almost%20exactly%20the%20same.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20practice%2C%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%2C%20along%20with%20belief%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20ability%20that%20differentiates%20between%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20was%20very%20choppy%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20swim%2C%20unlike%20the%20condition%20they%20had%20practised%20in.%20Yet%2C%20the%20two%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20anything%20deter%20them%20that%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20can%20lose%20your%20breath%20and%20composure.%20The%20water%20can%20be%20very%20unforgiving.%20You%20face%20certain%20life%20and%20death%20moments%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20that%20you%20must%20respect%20the%20process.%20Take%20the%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20hours%20were%20excruciating%2C%20their%20skin%20was%20completely%20burnt%2C%20the%20water%20rough%2C%20and%20their%20energy%20low.%20They%20kept%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20their%20goal%20for%20doing%20this%20swim.%20The%20crew%20also%20kept%20cheering%20and%20motivating%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20navigate%20the%20turbulent%20waters.%20It%20was%20a%20test%20of%20their%20mental%20and%20emotional%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20this%20achievement%20has%20a%20very%20high%20spiritual%20and%20cultural%20significance.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22h